    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/25750596/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_1848276211173759074.png",
                "id": "talent34806",
                "key": "Tempered Sword",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Tempered Sword"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>. Untuk penggunaan ketiga kali dari Skill ini pada setiap Ronde, mengakibatkan +2 poin DMG.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/25750596/d0e27bc7054292e95c673e6f491ff677_8822895476394057780.png",
                "id": "talent87592",
                "key": "Searing Onslaught",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Searing Onslaught"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 8 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>. Karakter ini menerima <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Elemental Infusion</span>.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Pyro Elemental Infusion</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> yang diakibatkan Karakter yang terpengaruh ini berubah menjadi<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/25750596/7f35364dc83b6694a3200aae53f6670f_3774093842231424540.png",
                "id": "talent3727",
                "key": "Dawn",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dawn"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Pyro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini, target berganti ke Karakter selanjutnya secara paksa</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] yang mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG di akhir Ronde (Jumlah penggunaan sekali, maksimum 2 tumpukan)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/10/1023623/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_2158852358159830475.png",
                "id": "talent21769",
                "key": "Pyro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pyro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span></strong></p><p>Setiap kali kamu mencapai Tahap Selesai di setiap Ronde, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> -1.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> habis.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/03/04/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_7520660219224705212.png",
                "id": "talent76673",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detail Peraturan"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
